---
title: Tex-Mex Pulled Pork Enchiladas with Grilled Cheddar Cheese & Sweetcorn
description: Let’s pull together an enchanted enchilada dinner to delight everyone at the table. They’re being wrapped up with all the goodies, like Tex-Mex spices, pulled pork and corn. We know just the thing to win you over (if all that isn’t enough already!), a cheesy enchilada sauce on top, perfect for a lasting, flavourful taste.
